<td valign="top">EMPLOYMENT OPPORTUNITY</p>
<p>Printing Ink Sales Representatives<br />
American Color Technology, a leading manufacturer of world class fluid printing inks, color dispersions and coatings for the printing and packaging industry is seeking highly motivated, energetic, aggressive, goal oriented individuals to fill our Senior Sales Executive openings. Previous printing ink sales experience is required.  We are seeking professional, self-motivated, sales-driven individuals to prospect, develop, sell and maintain business relationships with various accounts in your territory. <img alt="" src="http://americancolortechnology.com/images/stories/intense.jpg" width="203" height="303" align="right" /></p>
<p>Our ideal candidates will possess at least 3-5 years of direct fluid printing ink sales experience. Responsibilities include, but are not limited to the following: promote and grow account relationships, develop new accounts and sales, demonstrate aggressive sales growth and the ability to cultivate new accounts. Candidates must be able to quickly develop sales at new customer accounts as well as maintain current customers, excellent time management skills, and the ability to travel. Technical aptitude and the ability to work from a home office are necessary.</p>
<p>We offer a highly competitive compensation and benefit package including an incentive bonus plan, company car, cafeteria health and 401(k) plan with company-matching contributions.  This is an outstanding career opportunity in the printing inks and packaging industry while joining a dynamic, growing and profitable company.</p>
<p>Please submit your cover letter, resume, your printing ink sales history, and earnings history in confidence to Mr. Steven Talley, VP of Sales and Marketing Resources, American Color Technology, USA Inc. via E-mail,<br />
<a href="mailto:chadlackey@americancolortechnology.com">stevetalley@americancolortechnology.com</a></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
